subject: Football
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Garrett Wolfe, the national rushing leader, was held to only 28 yards, 130 below his average, and No. 25 Texas Christian won a Poinsettia Bowl mismatch against Northern Illinois on Tuesday night.
